testcase.title: Send a simple search query and check if 'Phase Not Applicable' value is present in Phase field in getTrialResults response.

I get a response with "Phase Not Applicable" in tag "Phase"

testcase.title: Send a simple search query and check if 'Phase Not Applicable' value is present in trialPhase column in exportTrialResults response.

steps.title: I am authenticated user accessing "SOAP" API

I pass a "format = MS_Excel and query = DBQueryForId_TrialWithPNA and offset = 0 and hits = 10 and sortBy = -trialPhase and expectedValues = CTI_Phase_01.xls" as parameter to "exportTrialResultsv2" operation
check the requested file is found in the following path "CTI_Phase_01.xls"
I get a response with "Phase Not Applicable" in column "Phase"
